com.camerontec.catalys.util.configuration.registry

Class Name

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.configuration.registry.Name
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Name>

    public final class Name
extends Object
implements Comparable<Name>
    The name of an IRegisterable. This is used as an index into IObjectRegistry.

    The name consists of a parent, a type, and an id.

    Parent may be null, in which case they are a root object. Id may be null if you wish to represent a singleton of the specified type.
